      <title>关于Volantis主题的一些配置教程</title>
      <link href="/2020/07/18/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8EVolantis%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
      <url>/2020/07/18/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8EVolantis%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><span class="p fas fa-hashtag green"></span> 关于小白修改Volantis的一些配置</p><a id="more"></a><h3 id="1-标签部件之添加公告"><a href="#1-标签部件之添加公告" class="headerlink" title="1. 标签部件之添加公告"></a><strong>1. 标签部件之添加公告</strong></h3><span class='p red'>位置(二选一)：</span><br>①volantis/_config.yml下的widget: 部分<br>②blog/source/_data/widget.yml<br><br><span class='p red'>代码：</span><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">announce:</span><br><span class="line">   class: text</span><br><span class="line">   display: [desktop,mobile]</span><br><span class="line">   header:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">     icon: fas fa-bullhorn</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">     title: 最新公告</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">     url:</span></span><br><span class="line">   content:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">     - </span>'写入内容'</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-导航栏之浏览页面时固定"><a href="#2-导航栏之浏览页面时固定" class="headerlink" title="2. 导航栏之浏览页面时固定"></a><strong>2. 导航栏之浏览页面时固定</strong></h3><span class='p red'>位置：</span><br>\volantis\layout\_pre.ejs 下的第8行<br>将此句<br><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">page.cover = theme.cover.display.others;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>删除或注释<br><span class='p green'>ps：在\volantis\layout\js\app.js中第48行开始，是关于页面中下移动时导航栏显示内标题的相关设置，可动也可不动</span></p><div class="note bug red">            <p>记得备份，不然头疼🤦‍♂️</p>          </div><h3 id="3-导航栏之导航栏与子菜单的距离"><a href="#3-导航栏之导航栏与子菜单的距离" class="headerlink" title="3. 导航栏之导航栏与子菜单的距离"></a><strong>3. 导航栏之导航栏与子菜单的距离</strong></h3><span class='p red'>位置：</span><br>\volantis\source\css\_layout\navbar.styl 下的第218行<br>将此句<br><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">margin-top: 4px - $border-card * 0.5</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>的第一个数字进行修改即可，4px效果可看我博客。</p><h3 id="4-导航栏之搜索icon颜色和输入字体颜色"><a href="#4-导航栏之搜索icon颜色和输入字体颜色" class="headerlink" title="4. 导航栏之搜索icon颜色和输入字体颜色"></a><strong>4. 导航栏之搜索icon颜色和输入字体颜色</strong></h3><span class='p red'>位置：</span><br>\volantis\source\css\_layout\navbar.styl 下的第148行(icon)和第157行(字体)<br>将此句<br><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">color: alpha($color-theme, 70%)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>的颜色进行修改即可，图中是主题的青色</p><h3 id="5-鼠标样式"><a href="#5-鼠标样式" class="headerlink" title="5. 鼠标样式"></a><strong>5. 鼠标样式</strong></h3><span class='p red'>位置：</span><br>\volantis\source\css\_base\index.styl 下的第5行后面<br>将此句<br><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cursor: url(https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sviptzk/HexoStaticFile@latest/Hexo/img/default.cur),default;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>还有在第89行后面<br>将此句<br></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cursor: url(https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sviptzk/HexoStaticFile@latest/Hexo/img/pointer.cur),default;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>补充上，这就是我博客的鼠标样式。另外还有如下样式<br></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cursor: url(https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/TRHX/CDN-for-itrhx.com@2.1.6/images/mouse.cur),auto;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    background-color: @theme_background;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cursor: url(https://images.cnblogs.com/cnblogs<span class="emphasis">_com/jingjingjingjingjingjingrj/1701449/o_</span>200415081944o_cursor.png),auto;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="6-全屏封面与归档图片的显示"><a href="#6-全屏封面与归档图片的显示" class="headerlink" title="6. 全屏封面与归档图片的显示"></a><strong>6. 全屏封面与归档图片的显示</strong></h3><span class='p red'>位置：</span><br>\volantis\congif.yml 下的第98行后面<br><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cover:</span><br><span class="line">  scheme: blog    // docs全屏封面, blog半屏封面</span><br><span class="line">  layout: focus   //关于封面上导航选项的样式。search (搜索), dock (坞), featured (精选), focus (焦点)</span><br><span class="line">  display:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    home: true    //这里是设置全屏是是否显示</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    archive: false //这里是设置归档页面是否显示</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    others: false  //这里是其他那些页面是都显示</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><span class='p red'>But！我发现修改layout的话评论区域就会GG</span><h3 id="7-音乐播放器"><a href="#7-音乐播放器" class="headerlink" title="7. 音乐播放器"></a><strong>7. 音乐播放器</strong></h3><span class='p red'>音乐库：</span><br>\volantis\congif.yml下的aplayer，大概第421行<br><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">id:  xxxxxx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此处填写在网易云收藏菜单页的地址链接上的id号(正常为十位数)</p><span class='p red'>样式：</span><br>\volantis\congif.yml下的aplayer，大概第423行<br><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">fixed: false</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><span class='p red'>①</span> fixed: false，原主题样式<br><span class='p red'>②</span> fixed: true，固定模式（看俺博客播放器）<br><span class='p red'>③</span> mini: true，迷你模式<br><span class='p red'>④</span> 自适应主题等等，具体请看<p>[<a href="https://aplayer.js.org/#/]" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://aplayer.js.org/#/]</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
